<title>PHILIPPINES: TABLE-Philex H1 net 320.4 mln pesos.</title>
<headline>TABLE-Philex H1 net 320.4 mln pesos.</headline>
<dateline>MANILA 1997-07-30</dateline>
<text>
<p>Six months to June 30.</p>
<p>	    (in million pesos unless stated)</p>
<p>    Net income		 320.4 vs 329.2</p>
<p>Note: Full name Philex Mining Corporation. Company said while net income was higher in the the first half of 1996, the income was derived from extraordinary gains resulting from the sale of investments, with mining operations posting a net loss during the period. It said profits in first half 1997 were derived from its Padcal copper-gold mine and from its share of earnings in its 81.8 percent subsidiary Philex Gold.</p>
<p>--Manila newsroom (63 2) 841-8936</p>
